trends, job creation, skilling, and labour market analysis.\",\"storyCount\":2,\"entityCount\":0,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-07-01T00:00:00Z\",\"stories\":[],\"entities\":[]},{\"id\":\"environment\",\"slug\":\"environment\",\"name\":\"Environment & Climate\",\"description\":\"Climate policy, environmental regulation, renewable energy, and sustainability in India.\",\"storyCount\":4,\"entityCount\":0,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-07-01T00:00:00Z\",\"stories\":[],\"entities\":[]},{\"id\":\"education\",\"slug\":\"education\",\"name\":\"Education & Skill Development\",\"description\":\"Education policy, learning outcomes, NEP implementation, and skill development programmes.\",\"storyCount\":3,\"entityCount\":0,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-07-01T00:00:00Z\",\"stories\":[],\"entities\":[]},{\"id\":\"semiconductor\",\"slug\":\"semiconductor\",\"name\":\"Semiconductor & Electronics\",\"description\":\"Semiconductor manufacturing, electronics PLI, and technology hardware policy.\",\"storyCount\":2,\"entityCount\":0,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-07-01T00:00:00Z\",\"stories\":[],\"entities\":[]},{\"id\":\"health\",\"slug\":\"health\",\"name\":\"Health & Nutrition\",\"description\":\"Healthcare policy, nutrition programmes, public health infrastructure, cancer care, and health outcomes in India and globally.\",\"storyCount\":4,\"entityCount\":2,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-07-01T00:00:00Z\",\"stories\":[],\"entities\":[]},{\"id\":\"infrastructure\",\"slug\":\"infrastructure\",\"name\":\"Infrastructure & Logistics\",\"description\":\"Transport, logistics, urban infrastructure, digital connectivity, and infrastructure projects driving India's economic growth.\",\"storyCount\":3,\"entityCount\":1,\"updatedAt\":\"2026-07-01T00:00:00Z\",\"stories\":[],\"entities\":[]},{\"id\":\"geopolitics\",\"slug\":\"geopolitics\",\"name\":\"Geopolitics & International Relations\",\"description\":\"India's foreign policy, bilateral relations, international organisations, trade agreements, and global diplomatic engagements.\",\"storyCoun